name: Calligraphy ToolBox
body:
### Welcome to the Calligraphy ToolBox

This project is an angular and javascript SPA to provide a number of useful calligraphy tools. Each of the tools will generate a PDF file which can be downloaded and printed for use with your next calligraphy project.


### Authors and Contributors
The author is @algenonq (Paul Rothwell).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
